    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "This is the patch that we had to apply:\r\n\r\n```diff\r\ndiff --git a/index.d.ts b/index.d.ts\r\nindex cd259e090441e6efc45c49fb0d4cee979545b750..576be59f2c499b04db16f0c0632503087a626f6e 100644\r\n--- a/index.d.ts\r\n+++ b/index.d.ts\r\n@@ -411,7 +411,23 @@ declare namespace algoliasearchHelper {\r\n      */\r\n     hierarchicalFacets?: SearchParameters.HierarchicalFacet[];\r\n \r\n+    // https://www.loom.com/share/60382a8ef084405e8d9e8b03db9f99e7\r\n+    // https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5715\r\n+    attributesToHighlight?: string[];\r\n+\r\n+    // https://www.loom.com/share/60382a8ef084405e8d9e8b03db9f99e7\r\n+    // https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5715\r\n+    attributesToRetrieve?: string[];\r\n+\r\n+    // https://www.loom.com/share/60382a8ef084405e8d9e8b03db9f99e7\r\n+    // https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5715\r\n+    hitsPerPage?: number;\r\n+\r\n     // Refinements\r\n+    // https://contra-work.slack.com/archives/C016ND05C2Z/p1687978374777379\r\n+    // https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5715\r\n+    facets?: string[];\r\n+\r\n     /**\r\n      * This attribute contains all the filters that need to be\r\n      * applied on the conjunctive facets. Each facet must be properly\r\n```",
